The validation corpus contained in /data/validation_corpus.csv is composed
of publicly available race results from official sources (UIL Texas,
TFRRS / NCAA, World Masters Athletics, USATF Masters). These results are
in the public record. The compilation and structuring of this corpus is
maintained by CoachLab for research and validation purposes.
